# Architecture

```text
backend/
  main.py
  core/          config, db, errors, indexes, logging, security
  dependencies/  auth.py (get_current_user, require_role)
  middleware/    (reserved)
  models/        tea, user, order enums
  schemas/       request/response DTOs
  services/      order_service.py (order + stock logic)
  routes/        auth, tea, orders
  tests/         pytest + conftest (fake DB)

frontend/
  src/           pages, components, routes, services, types, context
  tests/         Vitest (mirror src/); @/ → src/
```

## Folder responsibilities

| Area | Role |
|------|------|
| `backend/routes/` | HTTP endpoints (thin) |
| `backend/schemas/` | Pydantic validation |
| `backend/models/` | Persistence / domain enums |
| `backend/services/` | Business logic (e.g. orders, stock) |
| `backend/dependencies/` | FastAPI `Depends` auth |
| `frontend/src/services/` | Axios API clients |
| `frontend/src/pages/` | Route screens |
| `frontend/tests/` | Vitest specs |

Ignore `node_modules/`, `venv/`, `__pycache__/` in analysis unless debugging deps.
